SponosoredNews.title: CryptoCompare Releases Update to Exchange Benchmark for Q4 2019
SponosoredNews.body: The Benchmark ranks over 160 active spot exchanges globally to bring transparency and accountability to the cryptoasset exchange landscape by providing a framework for assessing risk. A grade is assigned to each exchange to help identify the lowest risk exchanges in the industry.
